description: [``botocore``] This release adds support for adding, removing, and listing SLO time exclusion windows with the BatchUpdateExclusionWindows and ListServiceLevelObjectiveExclusionWindows APIs.
[``botocore``] Provide support for vector map styles in the GetStaticMap operation.
[``botocore``] CloudWatch RUM now supports unminification of JS error stack traces.
[``botocore``] Adjust Vietnam PaymentVoucherNumber regex and minor API change.
[``botocore``] AWS WAF now lets you inspect fragments of request URIs. You can specify the scope of the URI to inspect and narrow the set of URI fragments.
